Grid = 1 : ITU-T DWDM grid 

n    = 5 : 

        Frequency (THz) = 193.1 THz + n * channel spacing (THz) 

        193.35 (THz) = 193.1 (THz) + n* 0.05 (THz) 

n = (193.35-193.1)/0.05 = 5 

Grid = 2 : ITU-T CWDM grid 

n    = -7 : 

        Wavelength (nm) = 1471 nm + n * 20 nm 

        1331 (nm) = 1471 (nm) + n * 20 nm 

n = (1331-1471)/20 = -7 

    
























 
 
